These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, camping, card-games, zinniaing
4 different games are played: backgammon, billiard, bridge, canasta
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, house, r&b, trance
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, zinnia, aconite, orchid
1. the person playing billiard is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
2. the fan of trance is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
3. the fan of r&b is the person playing backgammon##1
4. the person who's hobby is zinniaing is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
5. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
6. the fan of country is on the left of the fan of house##1
7. the person playing billiard is the person who growspoppy##1
8. the fan of house is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
9. the person who's hobby is zinniaing is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | board-games  | zinniaing  | camping | card-games |
| Game           | billiard | backgammon | canasta  | bridge  |
| Music-Genre   | trance       | r&b      | country | house      |
| Flower           | poppy          | zinnia     | aconite    | orchid     |

