.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, mystery, epic, time-travel
4 different pets are kept: mouse, ferret, bird, turtle
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, folk, indie, soul
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, ice-hockey, volleyball, water-polo
1. the owner of the mouse is on the far right##1
2. the fan of soul is the person who's sport is baseball##1
3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
4. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
5. the fan of soul is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
6. the person watching epic movies is the fan of indie##1
7. the fan of folk is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
8. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
9. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre      | epic     | family       | mystery | time-travel        |
| Pet          | turtle     | ferret       | bird   | mouse   |
| Music-Genre   | indie      | folk       | soul     | dubstep    |
| Sport         | volleyball | water-polo | baseball | ice-hockey |

