4. the person playing whist is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
5. the fan of ambient is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
6. the fan of funk is on the right of the person playing go##1
7. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
8. the australian is on the far right##1
9. the person who's hobby is card-games is the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |      4      |
| Game           | go   | scrabble  | whist | bridge |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | funk       | d&b       | ambient     |
| Nationality   | thai       | turkish    | dutch     | australian  |
| Hobby           | filmmaking     | card-games | fishing     | photography         |

