5. the turkish is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
6. the person driving the bus is the thai##1
7. the french is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
8. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
9. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |       3       |      4       |
