The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, poppy, sunflower, orchid
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, mystery, scientific, thriller
4 different pets are kept: fish, frog, horse, mouse
 1. the craftsman house is the person watching fantasy movies##1
 2. the colonial house is the person watching mystery movies##1
 3. the person who growstulip is the person watching fantasy movies##1
 4. the owner of the horse is the colonial house##1
 5. the person watching scientific movies is the person who growsorchid##1
 6. the craftsman house is on the left of the tower house##1
 7. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
 8. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
 9. the person who growssunflower is on the far left##1
10. the owner of the fish is on the left of the tower house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| House          | colonial  | farmhouse | craftsman     | tower |
| Flower           | sunflower  | orchid      | tulip | poppy    |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | scientific  | fantasy    | thriller  |
| Pet           | horse   | mouse       | fish       | frog      |

