The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, soul, hip-hop, r&b
4 different pets are kept: bird, frog, hedgehog, pony
4 different games are played: go, backgammon, billiard, chess
 1. the owner of the bird is the fan of soul##1
 2. the person playing chess is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
 3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
 4. the owner of the frog is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
 5. the fan of soul is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
 6. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
 7. the owner of the bird is the person playing billiard##1
 8. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
 9. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
10. the person playing go is on the left of the person playing billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage    | coffee | fanta     | iced-tea    | mirinda |
| Music-Genre       | disco | hip-hop    | r&b | soul |
| Pet         | frog   | hedgehog  | pony        | bird    |
| Game   | chess   | backgammon | go    | billiard |

