.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, juice, milk, water
There are 4 different favourite colors: amber, orange, green, chestnut
There 4 different types of food: raspberry, asparagus, avocado, spinach
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, jet-ski, scooter, skateboard
1. the person who likes green is on the left of the person eating spinach##1
2. the person drinking water is the person eating avocado##1
3. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
4. the person who likes amber is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
5. the person eating avocado is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
6. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
7. the person who likes orange is the person driving the bus##1
8. the person driving the scooter is the person drinking 7up##1
9. the person driving the skateboard is the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3      |     4      |
| Beverage      | water      | 7up         | milk        | juice      |
| Color           | orange | amber | green  | chestnut  |
| Food   | avocado    | raspberry     | asparagus | spinach     |
| Transport     | bus        | scooter     | jet-ski     | skateboard |

