4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
5. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person eating cranberry##1
6. the person driving the tram is the person eating plum##1
7. the person driving the snowmobile is the owner of the frog##1
8. the person who likes blood-red is on the far left##1
9. the person who likes blue is the person eating plum##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |      3      |     4      |
| Food         | papaya | plum | pepper | cranberry     |
| Color   | blood-red   | blue       | chestnut       | black  |
| Pet           | pony    | hedgehog    | mouse       | frog       |
