7. the malaysian is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
8. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person eating eggplant##1
9. the argentine is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3     |      4      |
