7. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the dannemann-smoker##1
8. the person traveling to berlin is on the far right##1
9. the italian is on the left of the fan of jazz##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| City          | boston | prague     | san-francisco       | berlin |
| Music-Genre   | rock      | jazz      | trance     | country   |
